org.eclipse.smarthome.core.voice.text

Class InterpretationResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.smarthome.core.voice.text.InterpretationResult

  • public final class InterpretationResult
extends Object
    Bundles results of an interpretation. Represents final outcome and user feedback. This class is immutable.
    Author:
    Tilman Kamp - Initial contribution
